name: Tilt the rays
description:
This photo make me impressed after long ride and i'm do again. 
Maybe i love photograph started at this moment.

I took this photo using digital camera. the camera is Fujifilm X10, so really small and old, but i loved this camera.

The photo take with zoom lens in the body and really good quality. So let's go out and takes amazing photo with any camera.
-
Captured in Pangalengan, Indonesia.
